## Rule Relationships

```
implementation-workflow.mdc (START HERE - ALWAYS)
    ├── pre-production.mdc (pre-prod guidelines - migrations, breaking changes)
    ├── nest-js.mdc (patterns & conventions)
    ├── testing.mdc (test conventions, factories, helpers)
    ├── project-structure.mdc (navigation)
    └── technology-stack.mdc (dependencies)

cursor-rules.mdc ←→ self-improvement.mdc (meta rules)
